<para style="p">

  <verse number="1" style="v" />But you, Titus, you must teach the things that help people believe the truth about God. 

  <verse number="2" style="v" />The older men should control themselves all the time. They should live in a way that other people respect, and they should speak wisely. They should also believe the true things about God, love others truly, and continuously do these things. 
